=begin pod
=head1 Gnome::Gtk4::R-Orientable

![](images/orientable.png)

=head1 Description

The U<Gnome::Gtk4::R-Orientable> interface is implemented by all widgets that can be
oriented horizontally or vertically.

U<Gnome::Gtk4::R-Orientable> is more flexible in that it allows the orientation to be
changed at runtime, allowing the widgets to “flip”.

